Note to cfengine contributors
-----------------------------

As part of a general code clean-up and restructuring effort of the
cfengine code, many of the direct references to authors in the code
has been removed. If you want explicit credits for a particular 
contribution, we can facilitate that by either doing so in this file
or at the top of the source file(s) in question. Please contact me
(skaar@waste.org) directly for this. The same goes for inclusion
in the above list.

cfng - development and contributions
------------------------------------

- Kent Skaar (skaar@waste.org), Luke Kanies (luke@madstop.com)
